WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.240
They leave the sickness of the forest below, only to meet the fury of the mountain.

2
00:00:06.940 --> 00:00:10.240
The storm-crust does not welcome pilgrims.

3
00:00:10.660 --> 00:00:15.240
It guards its secrets with claws of stone and breath of hurricane.

4
00:00:16.080 --> 00:00:24.280
The wind screams a physical wall of force that seeks to tear them from the cliff and cast them into oblivion.

5
00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:31.200
This is not a path. It is a test, a trial of will against the raw,

6
00:00:31.540 --> 00:00:33.580
unfeeling power of the world.
